high_descs: Turn left and again turn left move towards the fridge.
Pick the spoon from the fridge.
Turn left and turn right move towards the sink.
Place the spoon on the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the spoon on the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near fridge.
Pick up spoon from the desk.
Turn around and walk to the sink to your left.
Turn back and walk, then turn left towards the fridge.
Pick up the spoon from the top rack of the fridge.
Turn back and walk, turn right and walk towards the sink.
Put the spoon into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in the sink.
